      "content": "\"Woke culture\" is a complex phenomenon with both positive and negative aspects depending on how you view it. On the positive side, it has successfully brought much-needed attention to systemic inequalities and marginalized voices, pushing for greater social justice. However, the way it is sometimes expressed can devolve into performative activism or, as critics argue, an intolerant form of censorship against differing viewpoints. Ultimately, its impact depends on whether it fosters genuine dialogue or enforces ideological conformity.",
